RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Mukilteo, WA operates under a Mayor-Council form of government. The Mayor and seven City Councilmembers are non-partisan elected officials who serve four-year terms. Council members are elected at-large, so no specific divisions (wards/districts) are applicable. Joe Marine was re-elected as Mayor in November 2025. Tom Jordal is the Council President for 2025, and Jason Moon is the Council Vice President for 2025.
